OL,5, Bloomsbury says the Covid boom in      
OL,6, reading is continuing, as the Harry    
OL,7, Potter publisher reported bumper sales.
OL,9,F"The surge in reading, which seemed to 
OL,10,Fbe one of the only rays of light in the
OL,11,Fdarkest days of the pandemic is perhaps
OL,12,Fnow being revealed as permanent," said 
OL,13,Fchief executive Nigel Newton.          
OL,15,FBloomsbury reported pre-tax profits of 
OL,16,F#22.2m in the 12 months to 28 February,
OL,17,Fup 28% from the previous year.         
OL,19,FPre-tax profits were up 68% compared   
OL,20,Fwith 2019/20, before the pandemic hit. 
